## Step 2 — Interactive design with the user

This step **is** interactive and will iterate. Lead with your straw-man and refine:

- Confirm the **Aim** and the **spine** (the one organizing idea).
- Nail the **module architecture** — each module is a coherent unit with a gate; each
  task is one deliverable file with a unit test. Keep modules small and ordered so the
  dependency chain is mostly linear.
- Pin the **interfaces/contracts** precisely — these become the frozen Phase-0 tests, so
